        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes<strong> </strong>are fork tender, add the <strong>sliced courgette</strong> to the pan</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook, covered, for a further 4-5 min or until the courgette is tender with a slight bite</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
