      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the<strong> blanched peas</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook, uncovered, for 1 min further – this is your<strong> creamy sausage, pea & courgette stew</strong></p>",
